        <briefdescription>
<para>computes the half value of the authalic weight. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>This function computes the half of the authalic weight using the precomputed cotangent and squared distance values. The returned value is <formula id="36">$\frac{2\textbf{cot}}{\textbf{sq_d}}$</formula>.</para>
